subject: GENE
title: Topics for Technical Courses Taken on Exchange by Civil Engineering Students
description: Courses taken at foreign universities by University of Waterloo engineering students while enrolled in an international exchange institution, and reserved for courses without equivalents at the University of Waterloo. These courses are treated as technical electives in the student's plan. Such courses are reported on the student's transcript with their original titles in English showing as the topic. [Note: The grades for these courses will be either CR or NCR.]
